cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper is about policy distillation, a technique commonly used in deep reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the empirical analysis of the distillation techniques, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) if the analysis involves visual inputs.
